Document: RandomNumberGenerator
Path: godot/classes/class_randomnumbergenerator.rst
Summary: Provides a high-quality pseudo-random number generator.

Inherits: Object < Object

RandomNumberGenerator is a high-quality pseudo-random number generator. It uses the Mersenne Twister algorithm, which is known for its good statistical properties and long period.

This class can be used to generate random numbers for various purposes, such as simulations, games, or cryptographic applications. It offers methods for generating random integers, floats, vectors, and more.

Key Rule: The RandomNumberGenerator is not cryptographically secure. For security-sensitive applications, use a dedicated cryptographic random number generator.
