Document: RandomNumberGenerator
Path: godot/classes/class_randomnumbergenerator.rst
Summary: Provides methods for generating pseudo-random numbers using the PCG32 algorithm.

RandomNumberGenerator is a class for generating pseudo-random numbers. It currently uses PCG32. Note: The underlying algorithm is an implementation detail and should not be depended upon.

To generate a random float number (within a given range) based on a time-dependent seed:

GDScript:
```gdscript
var rng = RandomNumberGenerator.new()
func _ready():
    var my_random_number = rng.randf_range(-10.0, 10.0)
```
